==English==
===Etymology===
from [[generic]] + [[America]]
===Proper noun===
'''Generica'''
# features of the [[landscape]] such as fire hydrants, letter boxes, McDonalds, KFC, Wendy's, streets called "Main", that are the same wherever you go in the [[United States]]
===Quotes===
*''We were so lost in '''Generica''', I actually forgot what city we were in''-- John Perry Barlow
